top_projects.name: Decentra-Law
top_projects.description: A dApp that decentralizes the procedure of acquiring BAR Council licenses through on-chain relaying and verification of the documents and licenses .

top_projects.name: bookmydoc
top_projects.description: A Django-powered web app integrated with OpenAI that finds the shortest clinic from your location and registers an appointment at the time interval you prefer. It also finds the cheapest prescription based on your given prescription using a specially prepared Jan-Oushadhi database

top_projects.name: MedPlus
top_projects.description: An AI tool integrated with Whatsapp to take prescription orders along with verification with just a snap of it. A centralized dashboard is used to manually intervene and validate the prescriptions.
